      "message": "nit-nit; you may consider moving this to dsset.go in a more general form, if you anticipate that `eventbox/{add,remove}/duration` will be added in the future.\n\n```\ndssetDur \u003d metric.NewCumulative(\n    \"cv/internal/eventbox/dsset/duration\",  // or cv/internal/eventbox/dsset/duration\n    \"Duration of dsset operations performed\",\n    {Units: types.Milliseconds},\n    fields.String(\"op\") // add, list, remove\n    fields.String(\"parent\")\n    fields.String(\"result\") // the string representation of the error code.\n)\n\ndssetCount \u003d metric.NewCounter(\n    \"cv/internal/eventbox/dsset/count\",\n    \"Number of dsset operations performed\",\n    nil,\n    fields.String(\"op\") // add, list, remove\n    fields.String(\"parent\")\n    fields.String(\"result\") // the string representation of the error code.\n)\n```",
